      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Because of an editing error, an article on Friday about the shooting death of Rudolph Izzi, a loan shark and reputed mobster, included an erroneous reference in some copies to his place of residence. As noted elsewhere in the article, he lived in Brooklyn, not Staten Island.</p>
